cea, we understand the importance of selecting the right inlet and outlet sizes for your shell and tube heat exchanger. Our team of experts is dedicated to providing personalized assistance and guidance tailored to your specific requirements.If you have any other questions, please click the pinecone on the right side of the screen and feel free to contact our product experts at Repicea for a more comprehensive answer.\"}', '114.217.196.6', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.95 Safari/537.36', 1685514985);
