(797, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"32\",\"parent_id\":\"1\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type U-shape Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger Coated with Glass-lined Steel\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type U-shape Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger Coated with Glass-lined Steel\",\"en_detail\":\"The rough diameter glass lined pipe is used for arrangement, and then the glass lined elbow is used for connection to form a multi process structure in the pipe side. This structure can improve the heat transfer efficiency for the working conditions that are easy to crystallize and lead to material blockage. The glass lined elbow can be disassembled and the tube side can be cleaned regularly. High temperature heat transfer oil or steam can be used in the shell side for heating. This type of heat exchanger has high upper temperature limit and stable operation, and is suitable for reboiler or heater.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/d235cbc55e2d220cd85941f254c770a4fe67987f.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/1210d35ab29ce5a97207d9d3e1b90ca656f8d7a3.png\",\"carousel\":[],\"enable\":\"1\"}', '58.208.146.19', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.125 Safari/537.36', 1687942560),
(798, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"31\",\"parent_id\":\"3\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type High Borosilicate Glass Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type High Borosilicate Glass Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"en_detail\":\"Our company produces a new type of high boron silicon glass shell and tube heat exchanger. The tubes are made of high boron silicon glass, and the tube sheets are made of steel-molded PFA tube sheets. The sealing is done with threaded seals, ensuring a single-seal and easy disassembly. The shell is made of metal, optionally with an internal anti-corrosion lining, providing both internal and external corrosion protection.\\n\\nTraditional glass shell and tube heat exchangers have low strength, are prone to breakage and cracking, and have poor safety performance. Our new type of high boron silicon glass shell and tube heat exchanger offers improved safety, high-pressure resistance, and delivers better heat transfer efficiency and cost-effectiveness to our customers.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/199f825999028021293ff9d80df23b9ad5f6ec97.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/73253bb0fec905565a647d7140e76cd24730b01f.png\",\"carousel\":[],\"enable\":\"1\"}', '58.208.146.19', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.125 Safari/537.36', 1687942568),
(799, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"23\",\"parent_id\":\"2\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type Silicon Carbide Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger with Internal and External Corrosion Protection\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type Silicon Carbide Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger with Internal and External Corrosion Protection\",\"en_detail\":\"The new type of internal and external anti-corrosion silicon carbide tubular heat exchanger designed and developed by our company adopts double-sided molded PFA tube sheet, so that the tube sheet can be anti-corrosion both inside and outside. At the same time, in the shell side and inside the head of the heat exchanger, the anti-corrosion coating process of lining glass and fluoroplastics can be carried out. In this way, customers can not only use conventional cold sources or heat sources, but also use corrosive cold sources or heat sources, which greatly reduces the use cost of customers.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/dbcded9b2ef11cb4288f1aa79d39d6768854ca87.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/b0fdb77bc3133d1477ea3e56b8930973b3eb5cb7.png\",\"carousel\":[],\"enable\":\"1\"}', '58.208.146.19', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.125 Safari/537.36', 1687942577),
(800, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"22\",\"parent_id\":\"2\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type Silicon Carbide Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type Silicon Carbide Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"en_detail\":\"The new silicon carbide tubular heat exchanger that has been presented by our company adopts steel lined molded PFA integral tube sheet. This tube sheet has high material density, no deformation, and stable sealing effect, which better solves the tube sheet sealing problem of traditional silicon carbide heat exchanger. Two sealing structures are designed in one tube sheet, which can seal both the shell side and the tube side on the same tube sheet. If the silicon carbide heat exchanger tube needs to be replaced, just remove the sealing nuts at both ends, pull out the silicon carbide tube, and insert a new silicon carbide tube. It is unneccesary to remove the whole heat exchanger, which greatly reduces the maintenance cost when used on the customer&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;#039;s site. The shell side of the traditional silicon carbide tubular heat exchanger is made of tetrafluoro baffles. Due to the brittleness of the silicon carbide tube itself, it is easy to break when it shakes under pressure. Our company designed and invented to add a damping plate device to the device. When the silicon carbide tube is under pressure, the risk of shaking and breaking is greatly reduced, and the service life of the heat exchanger can be improved with an increment of heat exchange efficiency.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/ee9da82634b8906a6811b05c29d20523a1c740fb.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/e01d454e07830e3358f47b29e9ab5410e07c4d60.png\",\"carousel\":[],\"enable\":\"1\"}', '58.208.146.19', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.125 Safari/537.36', 1687942588),
(801, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"21\",\"parent_id\":\"1\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"product_21\",\"en_name\":\"New Type External Glass Lined Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type External Glass Lined Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"en_detail\":\"For the external glass lined tubular heat exchanger produced by our company, the outer wall of the shell side and heat exchange tube is coated with glass lined anticorrosive coating. The tube plate is also made of steel lined molded PFA tube plate, sealed with filler threads, sealed with a single piece, and disassembled with a single piece. Compared with the glass lined tubular heat exchanger with material passing through the tube side, due to the large space of the material side, it is more suitable for gas phase materials, which is more conducive to gas saturation, heat exchange and final discharge in the cavity. When the heat exchange medium is used in the tube side, a jacket is also set outside, and the heat exchange medium can also be used in the jacket, so that the materials can fully exchange heat inside and outside. Traditional glass lined floating head tubular heat exchanger generally adopts glass lined tube sheet explosive enamel or PTFE tube sheet, which is easy to leak in case of high-pressure working condition, high maintenance cost, and too troublesome to disassemble and assemble. The same heat exchange area is larger. Compared with traditional glass lined floating head tubular heat exchanger, it is more resistant to pressure, and it is not easy to shake and indunce enamel bursting when gas enters. It also saves the user&amp;amp;amp;amp;#039;s use cost.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/011659de709185512a42952330e5d69def272473.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230426\\/83f0684ba3fb6a0314a07d6f0ec8b362e17bc86f.png\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/69b83984b93dd30dd5aa2bab4dd6a918707f8d6c.png\",\"carousel\":[],\"enable\":\"1\"}', '58.208.146.19', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.125 Safari/537.36', 1687942602),
(802, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"11\",\"parent_id\":\"1\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger Coated with Glass-lined Steel\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger Coated with Glass-lined Steel\",\"en_detail\":\"Wuxi Revivingpicea Machinery Technology Co., Ltd. has designed and developed a new detachable glass lined tubular heat exchanger, which solves such problems of large volume, tube plate enamel bursting, difficult maintenance, damage and easy scrapping on traditional heat exchangers.\\nThe traditional glass lined tubesheet is easy to induce porcerlain bursting due to the stress of its steel billet, especially at the welding point between the tubesheet and the heat exchange tube. Once damaged, the whole set has to be scrapped, which increases the use cost for users. The new detachable glass lined tubular heat exchanger of our company adopts steel lined molded PFA integral tube sheet, discarding the traditional glass lined tube sheet, without the disadvantage of enamel bursting, and adopts a single connection and sealing system, which is more resistant to high temperature and high pressure. The glass lined heat exchange tube can be disassembled and assembled individually. If it is damaged during maintenance, it can be disassembled, assembled and replaced without scrapping the whole set. It is a truly reliable glass lined tubular heat exchanger. Our products are widely used in chemical, pharmaceutical and financial fields, enjoying a good reputation among our customers.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/6c6566689eea420745ed0de1fea6b41b33177948.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/6fcb2a9f5dce0a24c2112a980709c98ad4c468c1.png\",\"carousel\":[],\"enable\":\"1\"}', '58.208.146.19', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.5359.125 Safari/537.36', 1687942618),
