(819, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"11\",\"parent_id\":\"1\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger Coated with Glass-lined Steel\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger Coated with Glass-lined Steel\",\"en_detail\":\"Wuxi Revivingpicea Machinery Technology Co., Ltd. has designed and developed a new detachable glass lined tubular heat exchanger, which solves such problems of large volume, tube plate enamel bursting, difficult maintenance, damage and easy scrapping on traditional heat exchangers.\\nThe traditional glass lined tubesheet is easy to induce porcerlain bursting due to the stress of its steel billet, especially at the welding point between the tubesheet and the heat exchange tube. Once damaged, the whole set has to be scrapped, which increases the use cost for users. The new detachable glass lined tubular heat exchanger of our company adopts steel lined molded PFA integral tube sheet, discarding the traditional glass lined tube sheet, without the disadvantage of enamel bursting, and adopts a single connection and sealing system, which is more resistant to high temperature and high pressure. The glass lined heat exchange tube can be disassembled and assembled individually. If it is damaged during maintenance, it can be disassembled, assembled and replaced without scrapping the whole set. It is a truly reliable glass lined tubular heat exchanger. Our products are widely used in chemical, pharmaceutical and financial fields, enjoying a good reputation among our customers.\",\"image_small\":\"\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/6fcb2a9f5dce0a24c2112a980709c98ad4c468c1.png\",\"carousel\":[\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/6c6566689eea420745ed0de1fea6b41b33177948.png\",\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230630\\/2d4222867e24f6202a22bf890f399ee65fa00a7b.jpg\",\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230630