(854, 1, 'admin', '/admin/products.Products/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"22\",\"parent_id\":\"2\",\"layout\":\"horizontal\",\"name\":\"\",\"en_name\":\"New Type Silicon Carbide Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"detail\":\"New Type Silicon Carbide Shell and Tube Heat Exchanger\",\"en_detail\":\"The new silicon carbide tubular heat exchanger that has been presented by our company adopts steel lined molded PFA integral tube sheet. This tube sheet has high material density, no deformation, and stable sealing effect, which better solves the tube sheet sealing problem of traditional silicon carbide heat exchanger. Two sealing structures are designed in one tube sheet, which can seal both the shell side and the tube side on the same tube sheet. If the silicon carbide heat exchanger tube needs to be replaced, just remove the sealing nuts at both ends, pull out the silicon carbide tube, and insert a new silicon carbide tube. It is unneccesary to remove the whole heat exchanger, which greatly reduces the maintenance cost when used on the customer&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;#039;s site. The shell side of the traditional silicon carbide tubular heat exchanger is made of tetrafluoro baffles. Due to the brittleness of the silicon carbide tube itself, it is easy to break when it shakes under pressure. Our company designed and invented to add a damping plate device to the device. When the silicon carbide tube is under pressure, the risk of shaking and breaking is greatly reduced, and the service life of the heat exchanger can be improved with an increment of heat exchange efficiency.\",\"image_small\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/ee9da82634b8906a6811b05c29d20523a1c740fb.png\",\"image_mid\":\"\",\"image_large\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230529\\/e01d454e07830e3358f47b29e9ab5410e07c4d60.png\",\"carousel\":[\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230526\\/ee9da82634b8906a6811b05c29d20523a1c740fb.png\",\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230630\\/2a565e0