(916, 1, 'admin', '/admin/news.News/edit', 'Unknown(edit)', '{\"id\":\"8\",\"type\":\"opt0\",\"title\":\"Recently, our company went to Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for on-site inspection and exchange\",\"en_title\":\"Recently, our company went to Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for on-site inspection and exchange\",\"desc\":\"\",\"en_desc\":\"\",\"content\":\"Recently, our company went to Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for on-site inspection and exchange. During the visit, our team showcased our advanced products and demonstrated their capabilities to representatives of Xinhua Pharmaceutical. After a comprehensive evaluation and comparison of its original products, Xinhua Pharmaceutical has decided to replace its outdated products with our company&#039;s advanced solutions. This marks an important milestone for our company, demonstrating our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality products. We are pleased that Xinhua Pharmaceutical has recognized the value and advantages of our advanced products, &quot;said our company spokesperson, Mr. Gu. This cooperation is a win-win situation for both companies, and we look forward to working closely with Xinhua Pharmaceutical to achieve our common goals. Our company&#039;s advanced products aim to improve efficiency and productivity while reducing costs and environmental impact. They have been widely recognized and adopted by customers in various industries, including pharmaceutical, biotechnology and Chemical engineering. Through this new partnership, we believe that our company&#039;s advanced solutions will help Xinhua Pharmaceutical achieve its business goals and contribute to the development of the Chinese pharmaceutical industry.\",\"en_content\":\"Recently, our company had the privilege of visiting Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for an on-site inspection and exchange. During the visit, our team had the opportunity to showcase our advanced products and demonstrate their capabilities to the representatives of Xinhua Pharmaceutical.After a comprehensive evaluation and comparison of their existing products, Xinhua Pharmaceutical made the decision to replace their outdated solutions with our company&#039;s advanced offerings. This significant development serves as a milestone for our company, as it highlights our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality products.&quot;We are delighted that Xinhua Pharmaceutical has recognized the value and advantages of our advanced products,&quot; stated Mr. Gu, our company spokesperson. This collaboration represents a win-win situation for both companies, and we are excited to work closely with Xinhua Pharmaceutical to achieve our shared objectives.Our company&#039;s advanced products are designed to enhance efficiency, productivity, and cost-effectiveness, while also minimizing environmental impact. They have garnered widespread recognition and adoption across various industries, including pharmaceuticals, biotechnology, and chemical engineering.Through this new partnership, we firmly believe that our advanced solutions will assist Xinhua Pharmaceutical in realizing their business goals and making significant contributions to the advancement of the Chinese pharmaceutical industry.\",\"image\":\"\\/storage\\/default\\/20230409\\/4e892a43b308f2331730511823a6bb25d4a9392e.png\",\"enable\":\"1\",\"video\":[],\"create_time\":\"1687767425\"}', '49.66.59.229', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/115.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/115.0.1901.188', 1690879689),
