(932, 1, 'admin', '/admin/Faq/add', 'faq-添加', '{\"enable\":\"1\",\"rich_content\":\"1\",\"en_rich_content\":\"Wuxi Repicea: A Fusion of Innovation and Excellence, Delivering Unprecedented Heat Exchange EfficiencyIn today&#039;s industrial world, efficient heat exchangers are indispensable. Wuxi Repicea, with its unique technology and processes, continues to lead in the field of shell-and-tube heat exchangers.Superior Manufacturing Process: Our tube plates are crafted using the state-of-the-art steel-lined mold-pressed PFA one-piece forming technique. With the aid of a 1000T fully automatic press, we guarantee a one-time molding process, ensuring product quality and durability.Efficient Design: All of Repicea&#039;s shell-and-tube heat exchangers adopt a detachable structure. This not only facilitates maintenance and cleaning but also prolongs the product&#039;s lifespan. Moreover, our heat exchange tubes are all designed with a single-sealed process, ensuring impeccable sealing performance and preventing any leakage.Cutting-Edge Technology: The diameter of the steel-lined mold-pressed PFA tube plate determines the heat exchanger&#039;s heat transfer surface area. In this regard, Repicea showcases its leading technical capability. Based on specific customer requirements, we can produce heat exchangers with a single-unit heat transfer surface area exceeding 100 square meters, far surpassing conventional products in the market.Conclusion: Choosing Wuxi Repicea means opting for efficient, stable, and exceptional heat exchange solutions. We are not just product manufacturers but also a trusted partner you can rely on.For further inquiries or more detailed information, please click the pinecone on the right side of the screen to connect with our product experts at Repicea. They are ready to offer personalized advice and support, helping you make an informed decision tailored to your specific requirements.\",\"id\":\"50\",\"en_content\":\"Repicea said,\",\"en_title\":\"Why can Wuxi Repicea manufacture a shell-and-tube heat exchanger with a larger heat transfer area?\"}', '45.79.104.20', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', 1691502047),
