(34, 1, '', 'Why are companies from Fine Chemical Industry more suitable to choose glass-lined shell-and-tube heat exchangers and silicon carbide shell-and-tube heat exchangers from Wuxi Repicea?', '', 'Repicea said,', '&lt;p&gt;1&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;Companies in the Fine Chemical Industry often require heat exchangers that can handle highly corrosive and reactive chemicals. In such cases, glass-lined shell-and-tube heat exchangers and silicon carbide shell-and-tube heat exchangers from Wuxi Repicea offer several advantages that make them suitable choices:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;Chemical Resistance: Both glass-lined and silicon carbide heat exchangers have excellent chemical resistance, allowing them to withstand corrosive substances commonly used in the Fine Chemical Industry. Glass-lined heat exchangers are resistant to a wide range of acids, alkalis, and organic compounds. Silicon carbide heat exchangers can handle strong acids, alkalis, and other aggressive chemicals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;Corrosion Resistance: The corrosion-resistant properties of glass-lined and silicon carbide materials ensure long-term durability and protection against chemical attacks. This is crucial for maintaining operational efficiency and reducing the risk of equipment failure or product contamination.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;Thermal Performance: Both types