;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;By choosing glass-lined shell-and-tube heat exchangers or silicon carbide shell-and-tube heat exchangers from Wuxi Repicea, pharmaceutical companies can benefit from reliable, chemically compatible, and easily cleanable equipment that meets stringent industry requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;If you have any other questions, please click the pinecone on the right side of the screen and feel free to contact our experts at Repicea for a more comprehensive answer and personalized assistance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),
