(8, 'opt0', 'Recently, our company went to Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for on-site inspection and exchange', 'Recently, our company went to Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for on-site inspection and exchange', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Recently, our company went to Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for on-site inspection and exchange. During the visit, our team showcased our advanced products and demonstrated their capabilities to representatives of Xinhua Pharmaceutical. After a comprehensive evaluation and comparison of its original products, Xinhua Pharmaceutical has decided to replace its outdated products with our company&#039;s advanced solutions. This marks an important milestone for our company, demonstrating our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality products. We are pleased that Xinhua Pharmaceutical has recognized the value and advantages of our advanced products, &quot;said our company spokesperson, Mr. Gu. This cooperation is a win-win situation for both companies, and we look forward to working closely with Xinhua Pharmaceutical to achieve our common goals. Our company&#039;s advanced products aim to improve efficiency and productivity while reducing costs and environmental impact. They have been widely recognized and adopted by customers in various industries, including pharmaceutical, biotechnology and Chemical engineering. Through this new partnership, we believe that our company&#039;s advanced solutions will help Xinhua Pharmaceutical achieve its business goals and contribute to the development of the Chinese pharmaceutical industry.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Recently, our company had the privilege of visiting Xinhua Pharmaceutical, a leading pharmaceutical company in China, for an on-site inspection and exchange. During the visit, our team had the opportunity to showcase our advanced products and demonstrate their capabilities to the representatives of Xinhua Pharmaceutical.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;After a comprehensive evaluation and comparison of their existing products, Xinhua Pharmaceutical made the decision to replace their outdated solutions with our company&#039;s advanced offerings. This significant development serves as a milestone for our company, as it highlights our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality products.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&quot;We are delighted that Xinhua Pharmaceutical has recognized the value and advantages of our advanced products,&quot; stated Mr. Gu, our company spokesperson. This collaboration represents a win-win situation for both companies, and we are excited to work closely with Xinhua Pharmaceutical to achieve our shared objectives.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Our company&#039;s advanced products are designed to enhance efficiency, productivity, and cost-effectiveness, while also minimizing environmental impact. They have garnered widespread recognition and adoption across various industries, including pharmaceuticals, biotechnology, and chemical engineering.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Through this new partnership, we firmly believe that our advanced solutions will assist Xinhua Pharmaceutical in realizing their business goals and making significant contributions to the advancement of the Chinese pharmaceutical industry.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://110.40.139.205/storage/default/20230627/1962372b7b5c6db6318ea9df9568a6222391c263.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片1(1)(1).png&quot; data-href=&quot;http://110.40.139.205/storage/default/20230627/1962372b7b5c6db6318ea9df9568a6222391c263.png&quot; style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '/storage/default/20230627/1962372b7b5c6db6318ea9df9568a6222391c263.png', 1, '', 1687767425),
(9, 'opt0', '', 'Our company is proud to announce the completion of the largest single silicon carbide tubular secondary condenser in China, with a heat exchange area of 100 square meters.', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Our company is proud to announce the completion of the largest single silicon carbide tubular secondary condenser in China, with a heat exchange area of 100 square meters. This achievement highlights our company&#039;s commitment to innovation and excellence in the field of heat transfer technology. The silicon carbide tubular secondary condenser is a key component in the heat transfer process and is widely used in various industries such as chemical, petrochemical, and power generation. It is known for its high thermal conductivity, excellent chemical resistance, and excellent mechanical strength, making it an ideal material for high-temperature and high-pressure applications. Our team has tirelessly designed and manufactured this state-of-the-art silicon carbide tubular secondary condenser, which is the largest in China and an important milestone for us, showcasing our expertise in heat transfer technology. Our company&#039;s silicon carbide tubular secondary condenser aims to provide efficient and reliable heat transfer performance, ensure optimal process efficiency, and reduce energy consumption. With its large heat exchange area, it can High temperature and high pressure applications make it an ideal choice for a wide range of industrial processes. Our silicon carbide tubular secondary condenser demonstrates our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality products. We are confident that this new product will help our customers achieve their business goals and contribute to the development of various industries in China. This new achievement in the field of heat transfer technology is just one example of our company&#039;s commitment to innovation and excellence. We will continue to develop cutting-edge solutions to meet customers&#03