(10, 'opt0', 'Our company is pleased to announce its participation in the Anhui New North Card Chemical Co., Ltd. annual production of 200 tons of antiviral new drug intermediates project.', 'Our company is pleased to announce its participation in the Anhui New North Card Chemical Co., Ltd. annual production of 200 tons of antiviral new drug intermediates project.', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Our company is pleased to announce its participation in the Anhui New North Card Chemical Co., Ltd. annual production of 200 tons of antiviral new drug intermediates project. This project is an important milestone for both parties, reflecting our commitment to providing innovative and high-quality products to provide solutions for our customers. During the project, our company provided a glass lined tube condenser section, which has been put into operation. This key component aims to provide efficient and reliable heat transfer performance, ensuring optimal process efficiency and reducing energy consumption. We are pleased to participate in this exciting project with Anhui Xinbeika Chemical Co., Ltd. and contribute to the development of the pharmaceutical industry in China. Our glass lined tube condenser section is designed to meet the strict requirements of the pharmaceutical industry, with excellent corrosion resistance and durability Our company&#039;s glass lined tube condenser section is widely used in various industries, including chemical, pharmaceutical, and biotechnology. It is known for its excellent chemical and thermal stability, making it an ideal material for high-temperature and high-pressure applications. We believe that our glass lined tube condenser section will help Anhui Xinbeika Chemical Co., Ltd. achieve its production goals and contribute to the development of the Chinese pharmaceutical industry. This project demonstrates our professional knowledge in the field of heat transfer technology and our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality s