ssure applications. We believe that our glass lined tube condenser section will help Anhui Xinbeika Chemical Co., Ltd. achieve its production goals and contribute to the development of the Chinese pharmaceutical industry.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;This project demonstrates our professional knowledge in the field of heat transfer technology and our commitment to providing customers with innovative and high-quality solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;The project with Anhui New North Card Chemical Co., Ltd. is just one example of our company&#039;s continuous commitment to providing innovative and high-quality solutions to customers. We will continue to work closely with customers to develop cutting-edge products that meet their constantly changing needs and help them achieve business goals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://110.40.139.205/storage/default/20230627/b8fcff03e48052dd4517e1f13764254ff94084a3.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片3(1)(1).png&quot; data-href=&quot;http://110.40.139.205/storage/default/20230627/b8fcff03e48052dd4517e1f13764254ff94084a3.png&quot; style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 1, '', 1687848521),
(11, 'opt0', '', 'Our company has completed the customized U-shaped glass lined tube heat exchanger for Shandong Luxi Group', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;We are proud to announce the completion of a customized U-shaped glass lined tube heat exchanger for Shandong Luxi Group, a leading chemical manufacturer in China. This heat exchanger plays a crucial role in the chemical production process, showcasing our commitment to delivering high-quality and innovative solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;The U-shaped glass lined tube heat exchanger is designed to provide efficient and reliable heat transfer performance, optimizing process efficiency and reducing energy consumption. Its unique U-shaped design improves heat transfer efficiency and simplifies cleaning and maintenance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Working closely with Shandong Luxi Group, our team has designed and manufactured this customized heat exchanger to meet their specific requirements. Our U-shaped glass lined tube heat exchangers find extensive use in various industries, including chemicals, pharmaceuticals, and biotechnology. They are renowned for their exceptional chemical and thermal stability, making them ideal for high-temperature and high-pressure applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;The successful completion of this project showcases our expertise in heat transfer technology and our dedication to delivering innovative and high-quality solutions. We are confident that our U-shaped glass lined tube heat exchanger will help Shandong Luxi Group achieve their production goals and contribute to the development of the Chinese chemical industry.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;This project is just one example of our ongoing commitment to providing customers with exceptional solutions. We will continue working closely with our clients, developing customized solutions that address their specific needs and support their business objectives.&lt;img src=&quot;http://110.40.139.205/storage/default/20230627/a48d4de4776113d9004e06525f586288cca6dca6.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片4(1)(1).png&quot; data-href=&quot;http://110.40.139.205/storage/default/20230627/a48d4de4776113d9004e06525f586288cca6dca6.png&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 1, '', 1687848713),
(12, 'opt0', 'Our engineers are discussing the heat exchanger process with Jiangsu Guotai Chaowei New Materials Co., Ltd', 'Our engineers are discussing the heat exchanger process with Jiangsu Guotai Chaowei New Materials Co., Ltd', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our company is pleased to announce that our engineers have recently communicated and discussed the heat exchanger process with engineers from Jiangsu Guotai Chaowei New Materials Co., Ltd., a leading enterprise in the Chinese new energy lithium battery industry. This cooperation highlights our commitment to innovation and cooperation in the field of heat transfer technology. During the discussion, our engineers shared their professional knowledge in heat exchanger design and operation, and provided technical support and suggestions for Jiangsu Guotai Chaowei New Materials Co., Ltd. Our engineers have also gained valuable insights into the unique challenges and requirements of the lithium battery industry, which will help us develop better solutions for our customers. We are honored to have the opportunity to collaborate with Jiangsu Guotai Chaowei New Materials Co., Ltd. to share our professional knowledge in the field of heat transfer technology. This collaboration is an important step towards developing more effective and efficient solutions for the lithium battery industry Our company&#039;s heat exchangers are widely used in various industries such as chemical, petrochemical, and power generation. They are known for their high thermal efficiency, durability, and reliability, making them ideal solutions for widespread applications. We are committed to developing innovative and high-quality solutions to meet the constantly changing needs of our customers. Our cooperation with Jiangsu Guotai Chaowei New Materials Co., Ltd. is just an example of our continuous pursuit of excellence and cooperation in the field of heat transfer technology. Our company is committed to working closely with cust